    <item>
      <title>标普全球上调土耳其信用评级，暗示暂停</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/turkey-scores-second-s-p-credit-rating-upgrade-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于储备积累、通货紧缩和经常账户赤字改善，土耳其的信用评级今年第二次被标准普尔全球评级上调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/turkey-scores-second-s-p-credit-rating-upgrade-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 21:19:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚总统蒂努布不顾各州反对，坚持税制改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/nigeria-s-president-bola-tinubu-doubles-down-on-rejected-tax-reform-bills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布不会撤回已提交给议员的四项税收法案，此举可能会激怒那些有权有势的州长，因为他们的支持对于拟议的改革的实施至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/nigeria-s-president-bola-tinubu-doubles-down-on-rejected-tax-reform-bills</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 18:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对切尼发表暴力言论，引发强烈反响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/trump-invokes-violent-rhetoric-against-cheney-drawing-blowback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普暗示，如果他最激烈的批评者之一利兹·切尼亲自经历过战斗条件，她就不会那么“好战”了 — — 这位前共和党女议员使用暴力形象来形容切尼，并称其是一种威胁，这成为他与副总统卡马拉·哈里斯竞选的最新导火索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/trump-invokes-violent-rhetoric-against-cheney-drawing-blowback</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 15:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
